name: Willow World (coming into being)
description:
From the void emerged Willow World. A tree that has eaten an anti gravity pill so its branches and leaves no longer hang down. So yes, this means it is a willow tree that does not weep but it provides the stuff of life to the creatures who reside in Willow World. There is a lake made of liquid television and the world is lush with many critters. 

music by Quold and Sky Goodman
